targets.query: SELECT mean("value") FROM "snmp" WHERE ("hostname" =~ /^$hostname$/ AND "metric" = 'CPU RE0' AND "service" = 'Juniper CPU ACX') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval), "hostname"
SELECT last("value") FROM "snmp" WHERE ("hostname" =~ /^$hostname$/ AND "metric" = 'MEM_FPC') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval), "service" fill(previous)

list.label: Device name
list.name: hostname
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES from hostalive  WITH KEY = "hostname" where device_type =~ /$device_type$/

list.label: IP address
list.name: address
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES from hostalive  WITH KEY = "address" where device_type =~ /$device_type/  and hostname =~ /$hostname/

list.label: FPC Number
list.name: FPC_No
list.query: show tag values with key = "service" where hostname =~ /$hostname/ ;
